## Log Analysis Examples

Count total requests:

docker logs nginx_server | wc -l

Filter endpoint requests:

docker logs nginx_server | grep hello

Find most requested endpoint:

docker logs nginx_server | awk '{print $7}' | sort | uniq -c | sort -nr

